{"tid":503447,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港的士是最好的]上山頂收貴3倍車費 黑的司機遇放蛇警斷正","createTime":"2017-12-19T00:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T00:39:37.000Z","uid":51271,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ec379243c93593ca9c02d8a098ac638e4e7d540f","tid":503447,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T00:39:37.000Z","msg":"警方山頂分區人員今日下午約5時30分，在山頂及中區一帶展開打擊的士違規行動，其間派員喬裝乘客由中區花園道纜車站，乘搭的士前往山頂道118號。當人員上車時，58歲姓單的士男司機索價300元，較正常合理車資約為70元，貴超過3倍。<br />\n<br />\n其後的士抵達目地後，人員隨即表露身份，並拘捕該名司機，涉嫌濫收車資及沒有撥動的士計程錶指示器，他正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171218/57598943\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171218%2F57598943&d=OOlVbkzSc%2FpoKpTIQIzIf%2F6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=147ebc23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171218%2F57598943&h=bd009efe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171218/57598943</a>"}]}